en_162687_0	Met Department has announced that showers will occur at times in the Western, Sabaragamuwa, Southern, Central and North-western provinces.
en_162687_1	Showers or thundershowers will occur at several places in the Eastern, Uva, North-central provinces and in the Vauniya districts, particularly in the afternoon.
en_162687_2	Fairly strong winds about 50 kmph can be expected during showers.
en_162687_3	General public is kindly requested to take adequate precautions to minimize damages caused by lightning activity.
